Description: The origins and true nature of Pain, Naruto’s arch nemesis, are revealed.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 48
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: The battle for Cross Academy continues as Headmaster Cross enters the fray.
Title: VAMPIRE KNIGHT, VOL. 10
Author: Matsuri Hino

Description: Maka, an arms expert, wants to turn the Soul Eater, her living scythe, into the ultimate weapon for Death.
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 3
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: Ichigo and his companions press on in their mission to rescue Orihime, but two arrancars and Espada Ulquiorra stand in their way.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 31
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: No spoilers! After 13 years, Hirano’s epic genre mash-up reaches its conclusion.
Title: HELLSING, VOL. 10
Author: Kohta Hirano

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 2
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: In the final volume of the spinoff series, Yugi must duel to the death to save Anzu’s soul.
Title: YU-GI-OH! R, VOL. 5
Author: Akira Ito

Description: Negi, the boy wizard, vows to win the martial arts tournament and free his students from slavery.
Title: NEGIMA! MAGISTER NEGI MAGI, VOL. 26
Author: Ken Akamatsu

Description: Naruto learns more secrets from his past and moves closer to discovering the identity of his nemesis, Pain.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 47
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Alice wanders into a very different part of Wonderland in this interpretation of the classic tale.
Title: ALICE IN THE COUNTRY OF HEARTS, VOL. 3
Author: Quinrose and Soumei Hoshino
